m_employees = \n| website = {{URL|https://www.airheritage.in/}}\n| notes = \n}}\n'''Air Heritage''' is an [[India]]n [[regional airline]] operator owned by Heritage Aviation.<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://dgca.gov.in/reports/stat-ind.htm | title=Operator}}</ref><ref>https://www.aai.aero/sites/default/files/rcs_udan/Ms%20Heritage%20Aviation.pdf</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.airheritage.in/ebooking/home/ |title = Domestic airlines in India &#124; Domestic airline tickets Booking}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/other-states/commercial-flights-yet-to-take-off-at-hindon/article27029901.ece |title = Commercial flights yet to take off at Hindon|newspaper = The Hindu|date = 2019-05-04|last1 = Chandra|first1 = Jagriti}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url=https://m.timesofindia.com/city/dehradun/pantnagar-pithoragarh-flight-emergency-landing-dgca-starts-probe/articleshow/67946865.cms |title = Pantnagar-Pithoragarh flight emergency landing: DGCA starts probe &#124; Dehradun News - Times of India}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url=http://garhwalpost.in/oppn-alleges-poor-air-service-to-pithoragarh/ |title = Oppn alleges poor air service to Pithoragarh &#124; Garhwal Post}}</ref>\n\n==Destinations==\n{|class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:darkblue; color:white;\"|Country (State)\n! style=\"background:darkblue; color:white;\"|City\n! style=\"background:darkblue; color:white;\"|Airport\n! style=\"background:darkblue; color:white;\"|Notes\n! style=\"background:darkblue; color:white;\"|Ref\n|-\n|rowspan=3|[[India]] ([[Uttarakhand]])||[[Dehradun]]||[[Dehradun Airport]]||{{airline hub}}||\n|-\n|[[Pantnagar]]||[[Pantnagar Airport]]|| ||\n|-\n|[[Pithoragarh]]||[[Pithoragarh Airport]]|| ||\n|-\n|[[India]] ([[Uttar Pradesh]])||[[Ghaziabad]]||[[Hindon Airport]]|| ||\n|-\n|}\n\n==Accidents and incidents==\n*9 February 2019: The [[Pantnagar Airport]]-[[Pithoragarh Airport]] bound 9 seater aircraft's door opened midair.<ref>{{Cite web | url=https